ross-shell mixing also has a visible impact\non the $\\beta$-decay strength. Inclusion of the tensor force does not seem to\nsignificantly change, however, binding energies of the nuclei within the\nphenomenological interaction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2021 01:43:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
