action\nmodels, can be used in further studies on mass composition to obtain a more\naccurate image of the evolution of the individual fractions of nuclei as a\nfunction of energy on the basis of experimental $X_{\\rm max}$ distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2021 11:07:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-07"}
