lly, we\nshow that there is a fundamental trade-off in multi-path congestion-control\nprotocol design between efficiency, stability, and loss avoidance on one side\nand fairness and responsiveness on the other side.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2021 14:39:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-07"}
